{"tid":647926,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉多次毆打同居女友　休班警員准保釋候訊","createTime":"2018-04-30T09:05:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T09:11:35.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a1a8993f3e1dd0b56e8dbd9c18fabd729ae26445","tid":647926,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T09:05:44.000Z","msg":"休班警員涉嫌三度毆打前同居女友，前女友事後報警求助。涉案警員被控3項襲擊致造成身體傷害罪，案件今提堂，暫毋須答辯，押後至6月11日再提訊，以待辯方索取文件等，被告獲准保釋，期間不得接觸控方證人。當席律師指出，被告下次上庭將聘請私人律師。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，被告余展宏（35歲）於去年6月1日、7月11日及10月13日，在黃大仙鳳德邨某單位及尖沙咀柯士甸路僑豐大廈外襲擊黃綺婷，對黃造成身體傷害。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2063027/%E6%B6%89%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%A1%E6%AF%86%E6%89%93%E5%90%8C%E5%B1%85%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%8B%E3%80%80%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E5%80%99%E8%A8%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2063027%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%25AF%2586%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25B1%2585%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%258F%258B%25E3%2580%2580%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E5%2580%2599%25E8%25A8%258A&d=2a7ilcOh5yBi5M4PnETHk5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=13afad9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2063027/%E6%B6%89%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%A1%E6%AF%86%E6%89%93%E5%90%8C%E5%B1%85%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%8B%E3%80%80%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E5%80%99%E8%A8%8A</a>"},{"pid":"4b7ff4dbc7ac24bc7797bac0cb9913659de09cb1","tid":647926,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T09:07:11.000Z","msg":"休班警+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d251e6168cb75da5d000e6204c7ec9ef437a670","tid":647926,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T09:08:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1a970a96361b5c3c1fdc1638a4761edf04ebe77","tid":647926,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T09:11:35.000Z","msg":